<plot>Another of the series of Educational Pictures' comedy shorts headlining comic strip artist ("Gags and Gals") Jefferson Machamer. He joins a correspondence school to study drawing and sets up his desk in the post office where he can get his mail quickly. He has a section of private letter-boxes, and, as he opens each one, the artists models are seen there representing the various lessons.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?296614</url></doc>
